                        <div class="main-heading">
                            <h1>Restaurants, Wineries, <br /> Cafe's and More</h1>
                            <p>Meaford and the South Georgian Bay area have plenty of dining options for you to enjoy. From casual cafes and friendly pubs to sophisticated restaurants and local wineries, you can find a variety of places to enjoy the region’s flavors.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
