                            <div class="addons-desc flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column">
                                <h3>Coffin Ridge Winery</h3>
                                <p>Coffin Ridge Winery is a renowned winery located in the heart of the Grey County region in Ontario, Canada. It is situated atop the Niagara Escarpment, offering breathtaking views of Georgian Bay and the surrounding countryside. The winery is known for its unique wines crafted from cold-hardy grape varieties.</p>
                                <a href="https://www.coffinridge.ca/" target="_blank" class="btn learnmore mt-auto" title="Learn More">Learn more</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 mt-md-0 mt-5">
                        <div class="amenities-box d-flex flex-column h-100">
