                            </div>
                            <div class="addons-desc flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column">
                                <h3>Station 87</h3>
                                <p>Station 87 is located in the Meaford Firehall. Join us on the main level or upper-level dining room where you can enjoy our menu inspired by seasonal flavours. Join us on the rooftop patio, where you can enjoy panoramic views of Downtown Meaford. For more intimate gatherings, our private wine cellar offers a unique experience. Our Market side evokes a European marketplace. Grab an espresso and a sandwich made on our fresh bread while exploring all of the goods</p>
                                <a href="https://station87.ca/" target="_blank" class="btn learnmore mt-auto" title="Learn More">Learn more</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
