                                <h3>Fabricca</h3>
                                <p>Experience the quality of Fabbrica Thornbury’s regional Italian cuisine. Our menu features a diverse offering that is carefully curated to your taste. From the inviting dining room rooted by a wood-burning pizza oven to a buzzing patio, Fabbrica Thornbury is a rural gourmet retreat.</p>
                                <a href="https://mcewangroup.ca/fabbrica-thornbury/" target="_blank" class="btn learnmore mt-auto" title="Learn More">Learn more</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
